Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.98,0:00:05.81,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,This way, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.28,0:00:09.86,Nagi-Default,Akari,0,0,0,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.11,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,Akari-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.53,0:00:12.74,Nagi-Default,Akari,0,0,0,,Where are Hikari and the others?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.41,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,I'll go check again!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.41,0:00:17.41,Nagi-Default,Akari,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.54,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Manaka! Manaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.58,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.58,0:00:28.55,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Miuna-chan held me,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.22,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the feelings I lost flowed into me—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.22,0:00:34.38,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}like air into my lungs.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.39,0:00:38.72,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's because my Ena is\Ncrying out that it loves Hikari.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.76,0:00:40.93,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.35,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like taking a breath,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.93,0:00:48.36,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}my feelings as well as the feelings of other people flowed into me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.86,0:00:56.66,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like the love Miuna-chan's mom had for her father, \Nwhich brought her to live on land.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.37,0:01:01.08,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}As well as the love that Akari-san, Tsumugu-kun's grandfather,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.08,0:01:07.42,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}the candy shop owner Satsuki-san,\NKouji-niisan, and countless others had felt.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.67,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all fell in love with someone above land.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.01,0:01:14.67,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Lady was no exception.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.80,0:01:18.18,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she had tears in her eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.55,0:01:24.43,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The glow I felt in the sea was the\Ndissolved pieces of the sea's legend.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.60,0:01:27.60,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the legend of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.06,0:01:36.65,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sea God fell in love with\Nthe Lady only to be heartbroken.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.07,0:01:43.62,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the Lady had a lover above land before she became the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.33,0:01:48.42,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sea God could only hold himself at fault\Nfor pulling her away from her lover.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.67,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the Lady never once accused him of doing so.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.09,0:01:59.30,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, the deeper the\NSea God fell in love with her,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.47,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}the more pained his heart became.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.02,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seeing the Lady silently weeping,\Nunable to forget her lover,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.27,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sea God decided to return her to land.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.27,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the Sea God already knew.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.94,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The lover the Lady had left behind
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.70,0:02:22.99,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}was unable to bear his loss\Nand disappeared into the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.79,0:02:30.12,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, this led the Sea God to\Ndispossess the Lady of her heart to love.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.76,0:02:43.43,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she could love, the news of her lover\Nending his life would only succumb her to despair
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.77,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the Sea God feared\Nshe would follow the same fate.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.86,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Lady's feelings of love calmed the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.32,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hereafter, the sea would stay still.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.95,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a heart that has lost its love.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.99,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Manaka! Manaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.78,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.41,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.24,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,How's Manaka?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.62,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,Look, Chisaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.50,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Ena...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.84,0:03:18.97,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.30,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Chi-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.93,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Manaka, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.60,0:03:27.10,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,The sea's so pretty...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.11,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Miuna...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.74,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,A beautiful ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.41,Nagi-Default,Girl,0,0,0,,How pretty...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.53,Nagi-Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What's going on{ right now}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.54,Nagi-Default,Gramps,0,0,0,,It looks like the sea's starting to move.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.63,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.25,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.26,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.26,0:04:02.88,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,Wait, Hikari!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.39,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,Stop for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.56,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,If you try to force her out from there, she'll end up like Mukaido.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.73,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,So you're telling me to do nothing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.32,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,There's nothing...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.23,0:04:18.73,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I can do!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.11,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miuna was always looking at the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.16,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.91,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for Hikari.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.66,0:04:33.54,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.63,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,There should be a way to save her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.67,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,It's better not to act so rash.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.71,0:04:44.59,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,I'm going to check if anything's\Nhappened at the village.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.86,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,This ended up as another disaster.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.53,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,Uroko-sama...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.24,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.19,0:05:07.16,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,The Sea God told me to bring him to Shishio.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.29,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I want Manaka to fall in love with me."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.91,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I wished for.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.54,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to be the closest\Nto her and smile by her side.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.09,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd do anything to protect her smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.88,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, when I started living on the land,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.55,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}the one who saved me from\Nbeing overwhelmed by my fears
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.68,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}and stayed by my side was...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.43,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet I...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.93,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was blind to how you felt for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.64,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I love Manaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.23,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.44,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I love Manaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.61,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Again. {\alpha&HFF&}Again!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.19,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Again. Again!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.19,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hurt you so much...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.90,0:05:49.70,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Just... what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.87,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,You're... such an idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.71,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,How did you ever come\Nto like someone like me,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.75,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,while knowing my feelings\Nwere for Manaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.71,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Miuna, this can't happen to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.63,0:06:08.63,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because you loved Akari so much,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.89,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm able to see this happy\Nscene in front of me now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.64,0:06:15.64,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, I want Manaka to feel again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.89,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,But really, I was wrong...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.02,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,It's just like you said before,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.90,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,"If you didn't love anyone,\Nyou wouldn't have to be sad."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.15,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}When one finds love, another is brought pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.53,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there's no choice but to make someone suffer...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.91,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's what love really brings...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.58,0:06:36.41,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,...then being able to\Nlove someone is the worst!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.75,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Take it all away, Sea God!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.75,0:06:47.13,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Take every ounce of love\NI can feel away from me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.47,0:06:53.72,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3000)}In exchange, please save Miuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.94,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Manaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.15,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,It'll be okay, Hi-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.15,0:07:06.69,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.03,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Since Miuna-chan's feelings are...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.20,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.08,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really, Hikari's such an idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.38,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sea God is just as foolish too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.55,0:07:32.76,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sea God, why did you take\Nthe Lady's heart away?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.68,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because after all, she...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.77,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really want to let them know...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.56,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sea God.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.19,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.57,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Miuna...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.61,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want them to know what\Nit means to love someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.00,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,The spirit flames...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.00,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,No, the Sea God's consciousness!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.85,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to tell Hikari
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.85,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Shioshishio...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.64,0:08:26.52,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I'm glad I fell in love with someone\Nwho cares and cries so much for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.53,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.31,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,40)}Miuna...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.44,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the one who taught me, Hikari.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.40,0:09:13.07,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to believe it's useless, \Nor that you shouldn't love anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.65,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're right. It's not useless.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.07,0:09:21.83,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}Loving someone... isn't useless.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.75,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Miuna! Miuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.46,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.05,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,The Ladies?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.06,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,Sea God, why would you do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.82,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Sea... God.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.32,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.73,0:09:57.82,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,The Lady's feelings of\Nlove are inside the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.33,Nagi-Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to forget.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.25,Nagi-Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to forget.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.83,Nagi-Alt/Overlap,Uroko,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's coming from the sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.92,Nagi-Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't want to forget him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.25,0:10:19.39,Nagi-Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{\i1}But above all, I didn't want to lose the days I spent with you and our children
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.56,Nagi-Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{\i1}or my heart that loved you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.60,0:10:33.27,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,Such foolishness. Even a god would tire from hearing this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.82,0:10:43.62,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,Listen, Sea God. You took away her love without knowing who it was {\i1}really{\i0} for.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.20,0:10:50.58,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,And now you finally know of the Lady's\Ntrue feelings after they dissolved into the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.09,0:10:59.18,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,The spirit flames are\Nreacting to the Lady's heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.68,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,After acquiring Manaka to replace the Lady,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.68,0:11:09.69,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,the Sea God's emotions stopped flowing\Nout into the water, and the sea became calm.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.52,0:11:13.65,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,Without pain, there was\Nno need to make waves.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.65,0:11:19.45,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,However, while there was no loneliness, neither was there happiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.15,0:11:23.45,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,The spirit flames are also a part of the\NSea God's consciousness, correct?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.70,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.45,0:11:30.71,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,Until now, the spirit flames burned as what remained of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.96,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,But they most likely awakened to the Lady's feelings that dissolved into the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.55,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Uroko-sama...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.96,0:11:37.96,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.55,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,I am but a scale.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.01,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,A scale of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.80,0:11:46.81,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, just like the Sea God himself,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.81,0:11:51.48,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will love the Lady until the end of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.42,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.55,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.09,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Why are you awake?\NYou scared me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.26,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,What happened to the cold sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.26,0:12:28.01,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You're grown up, Miuna.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.02,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.64,0:12:36.40,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,A child made between the\Nland and sea lose their Ena.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.40,0:12:43.82,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Hence with the approaching crisis above land, \Npeople from the sea needed to be in cold sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.36,0:12:48.83,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,This is to preserve even the smallest hope of having descendents.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.66,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,However, Miuna is here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.08,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,And she has Ena.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.54,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,If that's the case, we can still have hope for what the future entails.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.34,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I-Is this all right, Uroko-sama?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.26,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,There's no use asking me;
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.26,0:13:08.01,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,I was not the one who awakened them.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.97,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Let me see Akira.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.02,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.77,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,How do you know about Akira?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.15,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Actually, how do you also\Nknow that Miuna has Ena?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.69,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.69,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You were the one who told me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.95,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You talked about how Miuna acquired her Ena and how Akira was born, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.36,0:13:32.33,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Your voice reached me,\Nas well as how you felt.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.33,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.54,0:13:43.63,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}A love that never changes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.89,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}A love that changes over the flow of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.22,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neither way to love is wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.81,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.27,Nagi-Default,Akira,0,0,0,,The sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.53,Nagi-Default,Itaru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.20,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The once calm sea is stirring!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.51,Nagi-Default,Man,0,0,0,,What's this? The sea stayed still until now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.30,Nagi-Default,Gramps,0,0,0,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.86,Nagi-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Bring out the ships!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.61,Nagi-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.49,Nagi-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hey! Hikari!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.37,0:14:55.41,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love comes from the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.95,Nagi-Default,DickB,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hikari!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.74,Nagi-Alt/Overlap,DickA,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Hikari!{Kinda ugly overlapping here, imo. - Lann}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.08,Nagi-Default,DickB,0,0,0,,{\an8}Glad you're back!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.50,Nagi-Default,DickA,0,0,0,,{\an8}I believed in you, buddy!{DickA and DickB on screen together again. Tears are coming to my eyes. :'3}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.87,0:15:06.88,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}A love that is gentle and kind,\Nbut also fierce and painful.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.64,0:15:16.60,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}But really, it's like a sea\Nwith everlasting love.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.07,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Manaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.53,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love is like the ocean.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.33,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Manaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.83,0:15:40.83,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.33,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.83,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.50,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Hey now. Weren't you worried about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.09,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,You're strong so it's fine, Hi-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.59,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.30,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Like ridiculously strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.93,Nagi-Alt/Overlap,Miuna,0,0,0,,Manaka-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.30,0:15:51.93,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.84,0:15:58.47,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,You're still the Manaka-san\Nthat I used to know!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.73,0:16:02.10,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.90,0:16:08.61,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,I should be the one saying\Nwelcome back, Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.86,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.24,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.07,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.70,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything starts from the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.59,Nagi-Default,Akira,0,0,0,,Great king squid!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.97,Nagi-Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Akira, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.72,Nagi-Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Whale shark! {can't really hear out this line >< srry}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.64,Nagi-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Get some good shut-eye?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.06,Nagi-Default,Man,0,0,0,,More like I didn't sleep enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.07,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Here, your rice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.82,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.98,0:16:53.15,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,So Ayakawa's dad hasn't woke up yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.15,0:16:57.78,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He's always been a worrywart so\Nhe'll probably continue cold sleeping.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.99,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I see. So I won't see him for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.99,0:17:04.00,Nagi-Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone has their own timing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.12,0:17:06.92,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.38,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Hm? Manaka's still not here?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.34,0:17:16.01,Nagi-Default,Kanama,0,0,0,,She said she forgot something,\Nso we can leave first.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.01,0:17:18.93,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Geez. Let's wait above then.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.10,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,Are things still the same\Nbetween you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.23,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Why are you asking suddenly?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.06,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,You should take her\Non a date some time.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.44,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,You finally know you two\Nfeel the same, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.57,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,Isn't it gonna be troublesome\Nif nothing progresses?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.32,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.99,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Everything's fine between us!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.86,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,Are you going to be like\NChisaki and hope nothing changes?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.62,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,No, I'm okay if things change.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.24,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.29,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,But, it's fine if things\Ndon't change either.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.29,0:17:44.87,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,It'll happen on its own.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.75,Nagi-Default,Kaname,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.47,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,I wonder if Hi-kun's mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.38,Nagi-Default,Akira,0,0,0,,Mamaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.55,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Akira-kun! You swam here again?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.55,0:18:04.27,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Akari-san's been complaining that you've been visiting ever since you could swim.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.27,Nagi-Alt/Overlap,Akira,0,0,0,,Backflip!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.19,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,The water's gotten fairly warm,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.40,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,but you might catch a cold\Nif you stay too long.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.90,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,You're not used to this, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.07,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Let's go up together.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.71,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Tsumugu-kun, good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.42,Nagi-Default,Akira,0,0,0,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.04,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,Want a ride?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.38,Nagi-Default,Akira,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.38,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,You're leaving today, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.47,0:18:42.51,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,There's just something I wanted to see\Nbefore I head back to the university.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.68,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,I wonder if Chi-chan's going to feel lonely.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.06,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,I'll be coming back during breaks.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.94,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.53,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,I like this view of\Nthe ocean from the land.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.28,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,That's something you\Nshould tell Hikari, not me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.66,0:19:03.74,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Wh-What I said just now\Nhas nothing to do with Hi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.00,0:19:08.87,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Let's meet again!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.13,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,Let's meet again!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.46,0:19:13.96,Nagi-Default,Akira,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.85,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Manaka and Tsumugu met,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.85,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\t(1290,2080,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFDFDFD&)}I thought they were led by fate.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.36,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,200,0,,{\an9}Hi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.36,Nagi-Default,Akira,200,0,0,,{\an7}Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.36,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.82,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Hurry up or we're going to be late!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.82,0:19:43.16,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Tsumugu, you can stay where you are though!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.78,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,Get over here, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.87,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fate and destiny don't exist.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.46,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything begins from your own actions.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.67,Nagi-Default,Sayu,0,0,0,,I don't look weird, do I?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.50,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,You look great.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.42,Nagi-Default,Sayu,0,0,0,,Do you think I look more mature {of an adult }like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.59,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,You're fine just the way you are, Sayu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.51,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,I'm sure Kaname-san would agree too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.68,0:20:14.35,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}While I led my life so far on land,\NI fell for someone from the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.56,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.32,Nagi-Default,Minegishi,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.36,Nagi-Default,Guy#2,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.99,Nagi-Default,Minegishi,0,0,0,,I think Shiodome's gotten prettier lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.16,Nagi-Default,Guy#2,0,0,0,,You still haven't given up on her?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.41,0:20:35.50,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tears I cried from my first love\Ndissolved into the gentle sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.38,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Oh, they're here!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.38,Nagi-Default,Sayu,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.18,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,{\i1\move(640,633,640,680,1000,1300)}The sea that took in everything...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.76,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Don't rush, Manaka-san—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.56,Nagi-Default,Miuna,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.77,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Thanks, Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.48,0:21:03.15,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now, I'll enter a new life\Nand make new memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.36,0:21:10.66,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,I'm going to visit my home in the sea, \Nso I'll be back a little late.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.12,0:21:14.04,Nagi-Default,Gramps,0,0,0,,It's fine if you return to the sea, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.54,0:21:18.54,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,The miso soup you make is too salty, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.30,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,I'm worried about your blood pressure.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.30,0:21:26.93,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Today, my mom's going to teach me how\Nto cook food that's good for your health.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.72,0:21:29.72,Nagi-Default,Gramps,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.89,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Tsumugu, you're going?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.15,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,I'll go to the station with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.15,0:21:37.65,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.27,Nagi-Default,Chisaki,0,0,0,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.98,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.19,Nagi-Default,Tsumugu,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to come visit\Nby the end of the month.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.19,Nagi-Default,Gramps,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.20,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,The end of the land\Ncould come at any moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.87,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,And we won't know\Nwhat'll happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.79,0:21:55.29,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,But with our will, we can\Nprobably change its course.{Italics?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.79,0:22:03.63,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,Sea God, humans are truly fascinating creatures.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.26,0:22:07.76,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,Even if they face pain,\Nor come across dead ends,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.51,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,they pick themselves up and\Ncontinue moving towards their dreams.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.22,0:22:15.60,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,And these feelings even have\Nthe power to overcome the impossible.{And such feelings even have the possibility to change the outcome of the impossible.}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.69,Nagi-Default,Uroko,0,0,0,,It appears the sea snow has stopped falling.
Comment: 10,0:22:29.99,0:22:35.00,Nagi-Default,,0,0,0,,#Eyecatch
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.50,0:22:39.88,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,Hey, do you remember, Hi-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.79,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,The Sending from five years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.79,0:22:46.01,Nagi-Default,Hikaru,0,0,0,,There was something you\Nwanted to tell me after, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.01,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}do{\i0} remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.01,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} were the one who forgot.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.81,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,But... even if I don't say it...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.27,0:22:57.23,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,I{already} know what you wanted to tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.73,0:23:06.03,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,They become one with the sea,\Nthe air, and overcome time.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.07,0:23:08.57,Nagi-Default,Manaka,0,0,0,,They're the feelings I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.41,0:23:17.50,Nagi-Default,Hikari,0,0,0,,This world is brimming\Nwith different kinds of love.
Comment: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.50,Nagi-Default,,0,0,0,,IN01
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:38.64,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,150)\be1}The waves pick up the dry pieces of coral,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:50.15,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,200)\be1}gently tossing and turning them to the sea shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:55.02,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:07.04,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}to the sound of moving sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.30,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Forget what tomorrow will bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:18.97,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Stir up your heart and call out to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:24.77,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}because I'll be here building a castle of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:34.36,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Forget about everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:39.66,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}because even if you can't call out my name,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:43.12,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}tomorrow will still come,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:48.46,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}and I'll be reminded of my sorrow each morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.59,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}But even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:09:00.35,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I'll gather everything I love and continue
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:06.48,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}until it gets swallowed by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:15.24,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Although my memories are failing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.03,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I call out to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:24.04,IN02-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}because I'll still be here building a castle of sand.
