Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.75,0:17:55.97,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}The faint sea breeze brushed my shoulder
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.97,0:18:02.66,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}as I could do nothing but watch
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.60,0:18:09.90,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}your small figure run off,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.90,0:18:15.40,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}unable to close the distance between us.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.61,0:18:25.87,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}Bathed in the soft sunlight, we laugh radiantly
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.25,0:18:34.38,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}in the photographs that hang from our classroom walls.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.80,0:18:42.30,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}We'll be reflected forever by those still waters
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.30,0:18:49.35,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}no matter how many tomorrows come.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.35,0:18:53.32,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}We don't have to change.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.32,0:19:03.74,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}Just gently hold onto those fragile feelings in our hearts
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.74,0:19:08.87,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}and hide them away...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.14,0:19:31.19,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}These waves ebb and flow
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.85,0:19:37.69,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}just like the distance between us.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.19,0:19:45.53,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}I want to know how you really feel
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.53,0:19:51.00,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}but you refuse to let me near.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.25,0:20:01.97,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}The time we have to share our dreams
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.97,0:20:09.47,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}is as fleeting and fragile as foam on the waves.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.48,0:20:17.94,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}We'll remember forever our pasts beyond these still waters,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.94,0:20:24.99,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}even if our reflections start to waver.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.99,0:20:29.08,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1\pos(640,57)}{\fnKG A Thousand Years\fscy180}''{\fnGlenns Hand\fscy100}I just want to protect you...{\fnKG A Thousand Years\fscy180}''{\fnGlenns Hand\fscy100}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.08,0:20:36.21,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}I stuttered over those words,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.21,0:20:45.05,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}as we watched the sun set over the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.10,0:21:02.03,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}Just like the view on top of this hill, things will change,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.57,0:21:09.48,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}and each enjoyable day will bring something new.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.08,0:21:17.33,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}Together, we watch the light dance on the water's surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.63,0:21:26.26,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}I just want to enjoy this moment.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.14,0:21:36.65,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}We'll be reflected forever by those still waters
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.65,0:21:43.74,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}no matter how many tomorrows come.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.74,0:21:54.96,Lull-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be2\fax-0.1}I'll bring back that dazzling smile of yours when we meet again,
